b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2569,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"A Platinum Showcase Is Now Live! 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia Dragon Guaranteed!","message":"<div>A Platinum Showcase started on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1635487200\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia dragon available at the start of this summon showcase is guaranteed to appear.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include the limited-time featured adventurers or featured dragon added in the Gala Dragalia showcase that is live at the same time.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon three times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1635487200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1637042399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5\\u2605 dragons eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5\\u2605 summon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/dfcfbefce5e423897fc3f2eeb6e55e3d.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>368<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>128<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,296<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>A powerful dragon who has existed since<br>primordial times. He wanted people and dragons<br>to have free will and potential, but he lost his<br>body in the fight against the Progenitor and can<br>no longer interact with the world.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b654508bf60eaeded9b2ecd23db805d32.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Cataclysm Beam<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>This skill has a unique gauge with three bars<br>attached to its skill button that is filled by<br>standard attacks and dragon strikes while the<br>user is shapeshifted. Upon use, this skill\'s effects<br>are based on the number of bars currently filled.<br><br>One bar: Deals damage to the target and<br>nearby enemies.<br><br>Two bars: Deals damage to the target and<br>nearby enemies and grants the entire team<br>a team defense amp.<br><br>Three bars: Deals damage to the target and<br>nearby enemies and grants the entire team<br>a team strength amp and team defense amp.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\"><color=#00008B>One Bar:<\/color><br>Damage: 410 \\u00d7 5 hits<br><br><color=#00008B>Two Bars:<\/color><br>Damage: 516 \\u00d7 6 hits<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbDefense Amp (MAX Lv. = 1)<br><br><color=#00008B>Three Bars:<\/color><br>Damage: 540 \\u00d7 9 hits<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (MAX Lv. = 1)<br>\\u30fbDefense Amp (MAX Lv. = 1)<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Shadow) Strength +120%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases strength by 120%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/808223f7e4cd602dd87951cc09df34592.png\\"><\/span><span>Almighty Rage II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 50% of the dragon gauge at the start of<br>quests and extends shapeshift time by 100%,<br>but doubles the amount of dragon energy<br>required to shapeshift. (The user\'s maximum<br>dragon energy will not be increased.)<br><br>Also, grants the user a dragon strike while<br>shapeshifted as Bahamut. This dragon strike<br>deals damage to multiple targets and enemies<br>near those targets.<br><br>The maximum amount of the dragon gauge<br>that abilities can fill at the start of quests will<br>be limited to 50% for the entire team.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/dcf493cf39fd262d1939a9bf61843c85.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>369<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>126<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,295<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The vestigial shade of Beast Volk, formed from a<br>portion of the amplified power conferred to him<br>by his Agito mask. His incoherent mumbling<br>retains the familiar bite of Volk\'s own rancor.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/8e762fc1fa1804dc9be5379a14026bd22.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lunatic Deliverance<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Grants the user the \\"Blood Moon\\" effect,<br>grants the entire team a team strength amp,<br>and activates \\"Skill Shift.\\"<br>This skill will become Lunatic Desolation<br>and be immediately readied for use.<br><br>Lunatic Desolation consumes Blood Moon<br>and all stacks of Moonlit Rage, deals damage<br>to surrounding enemies, and inflicts stun.<br>This attack deals additional damage based on<br>the number of Moonlit Rage stacks consumed.<br>If this skill has become Lunatic Desolation<br>and not yet been used when the user\'s<br>remaining shapeshift time runs out, it will be<br>used automatically.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbBlood Moon<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbTeam Strength Amp (MAX Lv. = 3)<br><br><color=#00008B>Phase II:<\/color><br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 0 to 3 Stacks): 1,098 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 4 to 6 Stacks): 1,618 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 7 to 9 Stacks): 2,244 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 10 Stacks): 3,600 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStun<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 7 seconds<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/65d6cd12143fa0ae6dd9c9d0d7ecd0b12.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Fangs of the Fangless V<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>increases strength by 100%.<br><br>Also, regardless of their attunement, grants<br>the user a dragon strike while shapeshifted<br>as Beast Volk. This dragon strike deals<br>damage to enemies in a line and reduces<br>their defense by 10% for five seconds.<br>This defense reduction will not stack.<br><br>While charging this dragon strike, the user will<br>be granted a stack of the \\"Moonlit Rage\\" effect<br>at set intervals. Moonlit Rage can stack up to<br>ten times.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d704441d2fe504b34ded414abd9ef9b2.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Plague of Weakness II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>increases the chances of inflicting any<br>afflictions by 100%, the duration of poison<br>and stormlash inflicted on enemies by 30%,<br>damage to poisoned enemies by 15%, and<br>damage to stormlashed enemies by 15%.<br><br>Also, regardless of their attunement, lowers<br>the user\'s affliction resistance by 150%, but<br>activates the following effects every 3.5 seconds<br>while they have the \\"Blood Moon\\" effect:<br>\\u30fbThe user is granted a stack of the \\"Moonlit<br>Rage\\" effect.<br>\\u30fbDamage is dealt to surrounding enemies,<br>and 10% of the damage inflicted is restored<br>as HP to the entire team. This recovery caps<br>at 10% of each adventurer\'s maximum HP.<br>The effect of the Dragon\'s Fierce Rule ability<br>will not apply to this damage.<br><br>When the user\'s shapeshift is undone, they<br>will be inflicted with poison for 12 seconds,<br>their dragon skill\'s \\"Skill Shift\\" will be reset,<br>and the Blood Moon effect and all stacks of<br>Moonlit Rage will be lost.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e91b31b3e5da42fa53e4fc2263861963.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>371<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>124<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,295<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The dragon maiden who guides all, now freed<br>from miasmal corruption, shines with newfound<br>luster. Inspired by the youth\'s hopes for a<br>radiant future, she hoists the standard of battle<br>to offer steadfast support to her warriors.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2a439e8a6e7f03f75118a7b5e2b7049d2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Holy Crusade<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and increases the user\'s max HP. If the user<br>is targeting an enemy and not using a skill<br>when their remaining shapeshift time runs out,<br>this skill will be used automatically, regardless<br>of whether or not the skill gauge is filled.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 330 \\u00d7 5 hits<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP +10%<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Light) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1143744471e52c225083bf356743039b2.png\\"><\/span><span>(Light) Oath of the Righteous II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against shadow-attuned enemies and enemies<br>with no attunement for 45 seconds every time<br>the dragon gauge fills by 10%. This increase<br>will not stack, and, after activating, this ability<br>will not activate again for five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragons at level 100, maximum bond, and unbound to the fourth stage. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note:<\/div><div>1. For more information about the Platinum Showcase, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select the Platinum Showcase and check the Appearance Rates section and the Details tab of the Showcase Info section.<\/div><div>2. The Platinum Showcase will be available during other showcases, including Gala Dragalia. You can move between showcases by using the left\/right icons on the Summon screen.<\/div><div>3. Performing a Platinum Showcase summon will not reset the appearance rate modifier increase for when a 5\\u2605 fails to appear after summoning ten times on another showcase, such as Gala Dragalia.<\/div><div>4. For more information, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info, Details, and see the Notes section.<\/div><div>5. Wyrmsigils cannot be earned from summoning on a Platinum Showcase.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1635487200,"prev_article_id":"2567","next_article_id":"2592","image_path":"","update_time":1635312863}}}'